            <thetext>Some virtualselectbox will have the arrow up &amp; arrow down shown
if option too many.

Expected behavior
Clicking on the up/down arrow button will scroll the option up/down.

Observed
Clicking on the up/down arrow simply close the popup option.
It happen on the latest version of firefox/chrome and also in IE.

Step to reproduce
1. Hover on any available option
2. Option will be highlighted
3. Click on the up or down arrow
4. Popup will close instead of scroll up/down</thetext>
